@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ucyggr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = (0.46 - v2)
    v0 = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.58) / 0.73) - 0.32)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.66) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.74)) * wp.exp((v2 + 0.96 - v0 + 0.64)))
    v2 = (wp.sin(v1) / (wp.abs(v2 + 0.59) + (tmp + 0.98 * tmp + 0.52)))
    v1 = 0.40
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
